column16: Sean Rodriguez homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.
Adam Frazier singles on a ground ball to left fielder Cory Spangenberg.   Francisco Cervelli scores.    David Freese to 3rd.    Starling Marte to 2nd.
Adam Frazier singles on a line drive to left fielder Jose Pirela.   Jose Osuna scores.    Adam Frazier to 2nd.  Jordy Mercer advances to 3rd, on a fielding error by left fielder Jose Pirela.
Joe Mauer lines out to left fielder Jose Pirela.
Ervin Santana grounds out, second baseman Carlos Asuaje to first baseman Wil Myers.
Jason Castro flies out to center fielder Manuel Margot.
Jose Reyes walks.   Asdrubal Cabrera scores.    Yoenis Cespedes to 3rd.    Wilmer Flores to 2nd.
Lucas Duda lines out to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.
Michael Conforto pops out to third baseman Cory Spangenberg in foul territory.
Travis d'Arnaud flies out to center fielder Manuel Margot.
Brandon Belt reaches on a fielding error by left fielder Jabari Blash.  Eduardo Nunez out at 3rd, shortstop Allen Cordoba to third baseman Cory Spangenberg.
Brandon Belt flies out sharply to right fielder Jabari Blash.
